snippet.title: Green Hell 1.0 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Green Hell has left Early Access and launched into 1.0! With a ton of improvements along the way, Creepy Jar proudly launch 1.0 and with it one of their most anticipated additions, Story Mode. Join Jake on his psychedelic-infused journey to navigate the deadly Amazon rainforest on his mission to rescue his lost love, Mia.

Available now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/815370/Green_Hell/
